  <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">A DTC brand spending $1.5M/yr runs MTA daily and MMM quarterly. MTA reports paid social at 1.2x ROAS. MMM reports it at 2.8x. The team suspects MMM is right &mdash; view-through impressions and brand lift are invisible to last-click &mdash; but doesn't want to act on a model alone.</p>
