  <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Two changes follow. First, MTA's social attribution gets reweighted upward in the daily dashboard so campaign decisions stop under-investing. Second, the next quarterly budget shifts $180K from search to social, where marginal return is now demonstrably higher. The MMM model is then recalibrated against the geo-holdout result so the next quarterly run starts from a stronger prior.</p>
